**Vicious Hag** | Unaligned Align | Limited
__Basics__
The Vicious Hag can win with any team, unless that team has wronged the hags. The Vicious Hag can attack another player.
__Details__
The Vicious Hag is one of the hags (`$i hags`).
During the night, the Vicious Hag may use their spell to attack another player. This power is not affected by redirections.
